-- ETF Securities Preparing to Market Funds in London in Industrial Metals
-- B y   C l a u d i a   C a r p e n t e r
-- 2010-10-11T07:46:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/etf-securities-preparing-to-market-funds-in-london-in-industrial-metals.html
ETF Securities Ltd. said it is
preparing to start exchange-traded commodities funds backed by
industrial metals.  The funds in aluminum, copper, lead, nickel, tin and zinc
are subject to approval of regulators and the London Stock
Exchange, ETF Securities said in a statement e-mailed today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  